{"msg":{"practice":[{"id":189,"question":"孩子不愿意做爸爸留的课外作业，于是爸爸灵机一动说：儿子，我来做作业，你来检查如何?孩子高兴的答应了，并且把爸爸的“作业”认真的检查了一遍，还列出算式给爸爸讲解了一遍。<br/>只是他可能不明白为什么爸爸所有作业都做错了。<br/><br/>上述故事中的爸爸运用了SCAMPER中的哪种思维？<br/>","type":1,"analysis":"Reverse<br/>以“检查”的名义，反来让孩子做作业，爸妈们可以试一下哦","pic":null,"difficulty":2,"knowledgeId":57,"sceneId":1,"del":false,"problemId":3,"sequence":3,"example":false,"practiceUid":"Y003T003C002A004X01003","score":30,"choiceList":[{"id":601,"questionId":189,"subject":"Substitute替代","sequence":1,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":602,"questionId":189,"subject":"Reverse逆向","sequence":2,"isRight":true,"selected":false},{"id":603,"questionId":189,"subject":"Eliminate消除","sequence":3,"isRight":false,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":540,"warmupPracticeId":189,"repliedId":null,"comment":"还是不太能理解替代这个选项","openid":null,"addTime":1488464216000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"晓露sheri","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyxPrKibibicpRzMx57Dib8I3mv4PIzcBzYNV8PZ3rMsjPExB3icliaYpuJL3KGBMEdqaAEPKN83ayRcnibO/0","discussTime":"2017-03-02"},{"id":202,"warmupPracticeId":189,"repliedId":176,"comment":"解释的很棒，受益匪浅，感谢，辛苦了","openid":null,"addTime":1487769215000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":"（重新思考了一下，来个自问自答吧）不应该理解为 替代。理由如下，知识点那页末尾提到：“SCAMPER是从产品和服务改进者的视角去运用的。需要从创新思考的起点，而非创新的结果去理解。”  针对这道题，孩子由被检查作业转变为检查别人的作业，这是父母创新思考的起点，而创新的结果是  传统写作业方式得到了替代。可以这么理解吗？","del":0,"repliedName":"Yovena","name":"神韵-Albert Han","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaELzmFHR1I2ZjVCx4aCrH9WAreVavWYKrT6hxPRmg4JicPIewicOfdBoxuhhSCnfDmEoev1COg0np4wQ/0","discussTime":"2017-02-22"},{"id":186,"warmupPracticeId":189,"repliedId":null,"comment":"提个建议，由于scamper的练习题相对难做一点，解析时是否可以不单说明正确答案的选择原因，也说说为啥不选择错误选项的原因，谢谢。","openid":null,"addTime":1487755436000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"Jessie Wu\uD83C\uDF80\uD83D\uDC98","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auH